Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 

Jo qudrat ne bikhere the
Bas meri raahon mein
Aur qismat ne sajaaye the
Meri nigaahon mein

Jaane ab kahaan milega 
Kahaan chhupa hoga 
Mil jaata toh rakh leta main
Apni panaahon mein

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Jhaank loon khud mein zara, sab kuch hai andar mere
Lehron pe milta nahin, jo gehre samandar mile 
Mehsoos hoga mujhe, jab khudko pehchanunga
Dil ke andar dekh kar, apni rooh ko jaanunga

Doobega‚Ä¶ Doobega‚Ä¶

Doobega toh tar jaaega
Har zarra mera
Varna tadap ke hi guzrega
Roz marra mera

Kya maine kabhi kiya hai
Thoda ishq bhi khudse 
Mil jaayega phir jo dhoondta hun 
Main darbadar kabse

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai
Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Woh sukoon mujhse hai‚Ä¶
Mujh mein hai sukoon‚Ä¶

snippet.title: Lee Cronin‚Äôs The Mummy | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Some things are meant to stay buried. #LeeCroninsTheMummy only in theaters April 17, 2026.

Hot off the record-setting resurrection of EVIL DEAD RISE, writer/director Lee Cronin turns to one of the most iconic horror stories of all time with an audacious and twisted retelling: LEE CRONIN‚ÄôS THE MUMMY. 

The young daughter of a journalist disappears into the desert without a trace‚Äîeight years later, the broken family is shocked when she is returned to them, as what should be a joyful reunion turns into a living nightmare.

The film stars Jack Reynor, Laia Costa, May Calamawy, Natalie Grace, with Veronica Falc√≥n. The film is written and directed by Cronin, and produced by James Wan, Jason Blum and John Keville. The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Macdara Kelleher and Lee Cronin. 

Cronin is supported behind the camera by a team of sterling film artisans, including director of photography Dave Garbett, production designer Nick Bassett, editor Bryan Shaw, costume designer Joanna Eatwell, music by Stephen McKeon and casting by Terri Taylor and Sarah Domeier Lindo. 

New Line Cinema, Atomic Monster and Blumhouse Present, A Wicked/Good Production, A Lee Cronin Film: LEE CRONIN‚ÄôS THE MUMMY. The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAXÔÉí in North America on April 17, 2026, and internationally beginning 15 April 2026.

Pernyataan Penafian Hak Cipta Berdasarkan Pasal 107 Undang-Undang Hak Cipta 1976, izin diberikan untuk "penggunaan wajar" untuk tujuan seperti kritik, komentar, pelaporan berita, pengajaran, beasiswa, dan penelitian. Featuring: Bobby Deol, Priyanka Chopra, and Bipasha Basu
Song: Saajan Saajan Teri Dulhan Sajaoongi 
Singers: Alka Yagnik, Kailash Kher
Music: Nadeem Shravan
Lyrics: Sameer
Produced & Director: Suneel Darshan

Saajan Saajan Saajan Mere Saajan Mere Saajan
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi Teri Dulhan Sajaungi

snippet.title: Bal Thackeray (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Amar Karnawal | New Haryanvi Song 2026
snippet.description:
Bal Thackeray (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Amar Karnawal | New Haryanvi Song 2026

NRI29 Productions bring you new haryanvi song 2026 in the voice of Masoom Sharma, penned by Amar Karnawal. Music produced by Pinna Music and Video shot by Chand Shivraj.

Song  - Bal Thackeray
Title - Bal Thackeray
Singer- Masoom Sharma 
Artists- Masoom Sharma 
Writer - Amar Karnawal 
Music - Pinna Music 
Composition- Masoom Sharma
Director- Chand Shivraj
Editor - Monty
DOP - Sushil 
Poster Design- B Town Graphics 
Project By - Vikas Rajana 
Producer- Sahab Bishnoi 
Label- NRI 29 Productions 
Special Thanks Haryanvi Association of Western Australia, Nven Verma , Anmol Rajput , Aman Sharma and Kiru 

Distribution Partner & Management : Ziaan Entertainment FZCO


Lyrics 

Mathe tika, aankh pe chasma

Kadd aur kaathi bhi s gach

Arre muh pe kehna, sukh t rehna

Saari bol chora sach

302 mai naam rahe se,
Maare aval kaam rahe se
376 lagdi dekhi s tere barge jaar ke

Re jor javani, dor tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chal bukal maarkay

jor javani, dor tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maarkay

Arey mar jau mitarr k khaatir
Pehla s yo karam mera
Arey hindu jaat aur chatri kom s, satya sanatan dharam mera

Vo bhagwa sujay raam n pujay
Charche saare yar ke gunjay
Bhagat singh se mohar lage maare kirdaar kay

Re jor javani, torr tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maarkay

jor javani, dorr tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maar key 

Arey Karanawalia chaam paad dye
Bhidne ka sahas na kr 
Chaanan bargi zindagi jee
Isne kaali umaavas na kr 
Re tere kuch be konya kisa 
Amar toh nyu hi lega jee sa 
Laage minute ka chotha hisa 
Dhar dyu chaati paad ke 

Re jor javani, torr tufani rakhi s singaar k
Bal Thackeray ki ju chhora
Chala bukal maarkay
